{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-yuzao-002__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-yuzao-002", "source_id": "xiaoya-yuzao-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·魚藻之什·002.1", "text_original": "采菽采菽，筐之筥之。君子來朝，何錫予之？\n雖無予之，路車乘馬。又何予之？玄袞及黼。", "text_normalized": "采菽采菽，筐之筥之。君子來朝，何錫予之？\n雖無予之，路車乘馬。又何予之？玄袞及黼。", "notes": "采菽 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-yuzao-002__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-yuzao-002", "source_id": "xiaoya-yuzao-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·魚藻之什·002.2", "text_original": "觱沸檻泉，言采其芹。君子來朝，言觀其旂。\n其旂淠淠，鸞聲嘒嘒。載驂載駟，君子所屆。", "text_normalized": "觱沸檻泉，言采其芹。君子來朝，言觀其旂。\n其旂淠淠，鸞聲嘒嘒。載驂載駟，君子所屆。", "notes": "采菽 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-yuzao-002__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-yuzao-002", "source_id": "xiaoya-yuzao-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·魚藻之什·002.3", "text_original": "赤芾在股，邪幅在下。彼交匪紓，天子所予。\n樂只君子，天子命之。樂只君子，福祿申之。", "text_normalized": "赤芾在股，邪幅在下。彼交匪紓，天子所予。\n樂只君子，天子命之。樂只君子，福祿申之。", "notes": "采菽 Chinese stanza 3."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-yuzao-002__004__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-yuzao-002", "source_id": "xiaoya-yuzao-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·魚藻之什·002.4", "text_original": "維柞之枝，其葉蓬蓬。樂只君子，殿天子之邦。\n樂只君子，萬福攸同。平平左右，亦是率從。", "text_normalized": "維柞之枝，其葉蓬蓬。樂只君子，殿天子之邦。\n樂只君子，萬福攸同。平平左右，亦是率從。", "notes": "采菽 Chinese stanza 4."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-yuzao-002__005__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-yuzao-002", "source_id": "xiaoya-yuzao-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·魚藻之什·002.5", "text_original": "汎汎楊舟，紼纚維之。樂只君子，天子葵之。\n樂只君子，福祿膍之。優哉游哉，亦是戾矣。", "text_normalized": "汎汎楊舟，紼纚維之。樂只君子，天子葵之。\n樂只君子，福祿膍之。優哉游哉，亦是戾矣。", "notes": "采菽 Chinese stanza 5."}
